    Note over Client, SafetyAPI: Flow 1: Remote Garak Scan (Production)

    Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    LLS->>RemoteProvider: Route to remote::trustyai_garak
    RemoteProvider->>DSPA: Submit 6-step pipeline<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token

    DSPA-->>RemoteProvider: Pipeline Run ID

    Note over KFPValidate, KFPParse: KFP Pipeline Execution (6-Step DAG)

    DSPA->>KFPValidate: Step 1: validate
    KFPValidate->>LLS: Validate benchmark config<br/>HTTP/8321

    DSPA->>KFPTaxonomy: Step 2: resolve_taxonomy
    KFPTaxonomy->>FilesAPI: Fetch taxonomy data<br/>HTTP/8321

    DSPA->>KFPSDG: Step 3: sdg_generate
    KFPSDG->>LLS: Generate synthetic data<br/>HTTP/8321

    DSPA->>KFPPrompts: Step 4: prepare_prompts
    KFPPrompts->>FilesAPI: Upload prompts<br/>HTTP/8321

    DSPA->>KFPScan: Step 5: garak_scan
    KFPScan->>vLLM: LLM inference requests<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: API Key
    vLLM-->>KFPScan: Model responses
    KFPScan->>FilesAPI: Upload scan artifacts<br/>HTTP/8321

    DSPA->>KFPParse: Step 6: parse_results
    KFPParse->>FilesAPI: Upload JSONL, AVID, HTML reports<br/>HTTP/8321

    Note over Client, RemoteProvider: Status Polling

    Client->>LLS: GET /eval/job_status
    LLS->>RemoteProvider: Check status
    RemoteProvider->>DSPA: Get run status<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    DSPA-->>RemoteProvider: Run state
    RemoteProvider-->>LLS: Job status
    LLS-->>Client: EvalJobStatus

    Client->>LLS: GET /eval/job_result
    LLS->>RemoteProvider: Get results
    RemoteProvider->>FilesAPI: Retrieve result files<br/>HTTP/8321
    FilesAPI-->>RemoteProvider: Report artifacts
    RemoteProvider-->>LLS: EvaluateResponse
    LLS-->>Client: Scan results (JSONL, AVID, HTML)

    Note over KFPScan, SafetyAPI: Flow 2: Shield-Augmented Scan (Optional)

    KFPScan->>SafetyAPI: Input shield check<br/>HTTP/8321
    SafetyAPI-->>KFPScan: Shield result (pass/block)
    KFPScan->>vLLM: LLM inference<br/>HTTPS/443
    vLLM-->>KFPScan: Response
    KFPScan->>SafetyAPI: Output shield check<br/>HTTP/8321
    SafetyAPI-->>KFPScan: Shield result (pass/block)
